					<a href="https://www.facebook.com/dialog/feed?app_id=180650338636285&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fgigaom.com%2F2011%2F04%2F08%2F10-things-you-never-knew-you-could-do-on-your-ipad%2F&#038;name=10+Things+You+Never+Knew+You+Could+Do+On+Your+iPad&#038;description=What+is+usually+the+first+thing+everyone+that+gets+a+new+iPad+wants+to+know%3F+Which+apps+to+get.+But+there+are+still+some+cool+things+that+you+can+do+with+your+iPad%2C+even+without+buying+a+single+app.+Here+are+10+good+examples.&#038;caption=GigaOM&#038;redirect_uri=http%3A%2F%2Fgigaom.com%2F2011%2F04%2F08%2F10-things-you-never-knew-you-could-do-on-your-ipad%2F&#038;picture=http%3A%2F%2Fgigaom2.files.wordpress.com%2F2011%2F03%2Fipad2-covers.jpg%3Fw%3D300" title="Share on Facebook" class="goicon icon-facebook"></a>
