	<a href="http://gigaom.com/2013/03/21/googles-motorola-wins-patent-for-octagon-smartphone-shape/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Google&#8217;s Motorola wins patent for octagon smartphone shape">Google&#8217;s Motorola wins patent for octagon smartphone shape</a>
	<div class="summary">
		<time class="time" datetime="2013-03-21T08:39:03-07:00">
			Mar. 21, 2013		</time>
		<p>Do you remember Apple's rounded rectangles patent? Well, this week Motorola obtained a patent for eight-sided smartphones.</p>
	</div>
</li>
<li>
	<a href="http://gigaom.com/2013/03/20/apple-sued-again-this-time-over-security-patents-by-intertrust/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Apple sued again, this time over security patents by Intertrust">Apple sued again, this time over security patents by Intertrust</a>
	<div class="summary">
		<time class="time" datetime="2013-03-20T12:46:07-07:00">
			Mar. 20, 2013		</time>
		<p>Intertrust has 250 patents related to digital copy protection software security and has licensed them to plenty...</p>
	</div>
</li>
</ul>
</div>	</footer>
