				<div class="comment-meta clearfix">
					<div class="comment-author-avatar">
						<a class="avatar-placeholder" rel="nofollow" href="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/36617335427b8dfb72d59716e4e7c32e?d=retro&amp;s=55&amp;r=pg"></a>					</div>
