				<div class="comment-content">
					<div class="comment-text">
						<p>You don&#8217;t have to purchase Xcode 4 to enable the additional multitasking gestures. Xcode 3, which is a free download to anyone who registers for a free Apple Developer account, can also be used to enable those gestures.</p>
