						<cite><a href='http://ggeoffre.wordpress.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Geoffrey Goetz</a></cite>
						<a href="http://gigaom.com/2011/04/08/10-things-you-never-knew-you-could-do-on-your-ipad/#comment-615645" class="comment-permalink">Saturday, April 9 2011</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="comment-content">
					<div class="comment-text">
						<p>While you can still download the older Xcode as a member of the ADC, I did not try it with that version.  Moving forward, Apple will likely only support new iOS versions with Xcode 4.  Which is why I was hesitant to suggest the older version.</p>
					</div>
