					<div class="comment-text">
						<p>Yeah, I realize that.  In the keyboard section I mentioned two cool keyboard facts.  And in both cases, the apps purchased unlock features rather than be features on their own.  In the later, you could download the old version of Xcode for free, even though I did not specifically mention that fact.  But yes, the ice is thin in those two cases.</p>
