				<div class="comment-meta clearfix">
					<div class="comment-author-avatar">
						<a class="avatar-placeholder" rel="nofollow" href="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/a2a614b47896288eda921facaa4dc14c?d=retro&amp;s=55&amp;r=pg"></a>					</div>
					<div class="comment-info">
						<cite>cd</cite>
						<a href="http://gigaom.com/2011/04/08/10-things-you-never-knew-you-could-do-on-your-ipad/#comment-615789" class="comment-permalink">Sunday, April 10 2011</a>
