				<div class="comment-content">
					<div class="comment-text">
						<p>there is something missing. you can allign every text in every text app, notes too, to the right. all you have to do is adding the hebrew keyboard. go to systempreferences-&gt;general-&gt;keyboard-&gt;international keyboards. </p>
<p>than, you tap on a word and press the arrows.</p>
